First define the path of the webserver cgi-bin directory by editing the line Makefile

bindir = /usr/local/apache2/cgi-bin 

Then edit the 3 X #define in the source files.
The source file has a detailed comment that documents everything.

The fast track steps are

	Edit the 3 defines in the .c files

	Edit the Makefile and run

    make
    
    make install

For more information see
http://www.lavrsen.dk/twiki/bin/view/Motion/MjpegProxyGrab
